* [[Louis XV of France|Louis XV]]  (1710&nbsp;<U+2013> 1774),
* [[Louis XVI of France|Louis XVI]] (1754&nbsp;<U+2013> 1793) and [[Marie Antoinette]] (1755&nbsp;<U+2013> 1793)
* [[Louis XVII of France|Louis XVII]] (1785<U+2013>1795) (Only his heart. His body was dumped into a mass grave)
* [[Louis XVIII of France|Louis XVIII]] (1755<U+2013>1824)

===Other royalty and nobility===

*[[Nicolas Henri, Duke of Orl<U+00E9>ans]] (1607<U+2013>1611), son of Henry IV,
*[[Gaston, Duke of Orl<U+00E9>ans]] (1608<U+2013>1660), son of Henry IV,
**[[Marie de Bourbon, Duchess of Montpensier]] (1605<U+2013>1627), wife of Gaston,
